<i> But like you're</i> really<i> trying</i>
<i> to sell a car.</i>

10:12.754 --> 10:15.421
<i> Oh. Okay. Mm-hmm.</i>

10:15.423 --> 10:17.322
<i> ¶ there's no place better</i>
<i> than big al's car ¶</i>

